               <p>6. 
               
                  <persName id="t17901208-6-defend104" type="defendantName">
                     SAMUEL 
                     WITHERS
                  <interp inst="t17901208-6-defend104" type="surname" value="WITHERS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17901208-6-defend104" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17901208-6-defend104" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted, for <rs id="t17901208-6-off27" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17901208-6-off27" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17901208-6-off27" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t17901208-6-cd28" type="crimeDate">4th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17901208-6-off27 t17901208-6-cd28"></join> last, feloniously and falsely did make, forge, and counterfeit, and cause and procure to be falsely made, forged, and counterfeited, and willingly act and assist in the false making, forging, and counterfeiting, a certain order for the payment of money, dated 4th November, 1790, with the name W. Buller, thereto subscribed, purporting to have been signed by 
                     <persName id="t17901208-6-person105">
                        Wm.
                         Buller
                     <interp inst="t17901208-6-person105" type="surname" value="Buller"></interp>
