                        <interp inst="t17901208-6-person108" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , by the name and description of Mess. Biddulph, and Co. for the payment of the sum of sixty pounds, to bearer, with intention to defraud the said 
                     
                        <persName id="t17901208-6-victim110" type="victimName">
                           Francis 
                           Biddulph
                        <interp inst="t17901208-6-victim110" type="surname" value="Biddulph"></interp>
